        "description": {
            "value": "<p><em><strong>Prerequisite:</strong> Telekinetic Burst</em></p>\n<p>You manipulate the Force in a 60-foot radius centered on a point you choose within range. Each creature in that area must make a Constitution saving throw. On a failed save, a creature takes 12d6 force damage, is knocked prone, and moved 5 feet in a direction of your choice. On a successful save, it takes half as much damage and isn&rsquo;t knocked prone or moved.</p>\n<p><em><strong>Force Potency.</strong></em>&nbsp;When you cast this power using a force slot of 9th level, the damage increases by 2d6.</p>",
